Keep track of time with an integrated clock that complements the dramatic design.

Quickly access Google search directly from your new tab for convenient browsing.

The clash of Gojo’s infinite power and Sukuna’s cursed wrath fills your screen with action.

Smooth, lag-free performance that ensures your browsing experience is seamless.

Perfect for Jujutsu Kaisen Fans:
Celebrate the iconic battle between two of the series’ most powerful characters.
